    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >您将在满目疮痍的南极洲中挣扎求生，并逐步揭开隐藏的秘密。步步为营的探索冒险，静谧内敛的荒芜氛围，与感伤迷人的故事融合在一起，为您提供独一无二的游戏体验。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>[h1]<strong>遥远未来的南极——最神奇，也是最危险的地方</strong>[/h1]<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你的最终目的地——南极点。但你将遇到最极端的气候和致命的危险，保持警惕，善用你的体力，活用你的智慧，或许……也要相信你的直觉。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>・暴风雪</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >无情的暴风雪会挟裹着危险物体向你袭来，利用墙壁或其他障碍物来躲避。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>・极寒天气</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >南极的气温有时会降至零下30摄氏度以下，持续暴露在严寒中，体力会迅速下降。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>・辐射危险</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >过去的战争导致南极受到辐射污染，这甚至会导致防护服出现故障。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>・病毒感染</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >南极正遭受病毒的侵袭，你需要在前进途中启动消毒装置，净化受污染区域。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2054310/extras/a40276f3029cfb51cbb711194d61c887.poster.avif?t=1769617465\" width=616 height=222 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2054310/extras/a40276f3029cfb51cbb711194d61c887.webm?t=1769617465\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2054310/extras/a40276f3029cfb51cbb711194d61c887.mp4?t=1769617465\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>[h1]<strong>生存下去——利用一切手段</strong>[/h1]<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你要利用人类文明残骸所遗留下来的“制造”及“建造”技术，使用沿途找到的石头和木材等资源，以及失落科技的残存部件，来制造旅途所需的各类物品。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > <strong>・收集素材——时刻注意体力</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >如何平衡收集物资和保存体力，是游戏中的必修课，请在时刻留心体力的同时，有策略地收集资源。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>・制造——复原失落技术</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >当找到一件看似有用的物品时，可以使用高性能3D打印机进行扫描，并添加到制造清单中。通过不同物品的有机组合，可以获得大型的复杂装置。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>・组装——随时随地</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在某些情况下，可以对物品进行现场组装。所以需要做好预案，提前制造出物品，紧要关头时才可马上组装。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2054310/extras/218b55fc958d68abfe069daa99096d6e.poster.avif?t=1769617465\" width=616 height=222 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2054310/extras/218b55fc958d68abfe069daa99096d6e.webm?t=1769617465\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2054310/extras/218b55fc958d68abfe069daa99096d6e.mp4?t=1769617465\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>[h5]<strong>故事梗概</strong>[/h5]<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >故事发生在遥远的未来——公元30世纪。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >由于致命病毒的蔓延、严重的粮食危机、极端的天气及无休止的战争，导致地球人口剧减，逐渐沦为废墟，昔日繁荣早已不复存在。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >就在这满目疮痍之际，世界各国突然接收到了一道来自南极点的神秘信号。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >这是暗示着此处蕴含有富饶资源的一线微弱的希望之光。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >于是人类把最后的希望寄托在主人公——一个孩子身上，</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >将其送往环境已经被严重污染的南极点。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >究竟是谁发出了这道信号？其目的又是什么？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >而决定人类未来命运的，又会是什么？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2054310/extras/673677cc2408f1978755f41ed05a8777.avif?t=1769617465\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2054310/extras_big/673677cc2408f1978755f41ed05a8777.avif?t=1769617465 width=1560 height=1106 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2054310/extras/248d85bd25c69b35635344d25aa7b783.avif?t=1769617465\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2054310/extras_big/248d85bd25c69b35635344d25aa7b783.webp?t=1769617465 width=1560 height=1108 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
